<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She has jetted to Marbella for a girls' holiday after ringing in her 25th birthday.</p>

<p>And Chloe Ferry was sure to set pulses racing as she soaked up the sun at a luxury resort during her Spanish getaway on Friday.</p>

<p>The Geordie Shore star, 24, looked sensational in a yellow leopard-print bikini that showed off a glimpse of her ample assets.</p>

<p>Wow! Chloe Ferry set pulses racing in a yellow leopard print bikini as she soaked up the sun during her Marbella trip on Friday</p>

<p>Chloe's thong bottoms were cut high on her waist to highlight her pert posterior, while she opted to go barefoot to walk to her sun lounger.</p>

<p>The reality star's blonde locks were brushed into a sleek straight style and she pulled her hair back into a messy bun underneath her large straw hat. </p>

<p>Chloe completed her look by shielding her eyes with a pair of chic shades, and she looked relaxed as she soaked up the sun.</p>

